<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Phase 0: Python Warm-up on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/</link><description>Recent content in Phase 0: Python Warm-up on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>1. Install and Run the App</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/1-install-and-run/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/1-install-and-run/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="set-up-the-python-environment"&gt;
