&lt;h2 id="set-your-splunk-credentials"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Set Your Splunk Credentials&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#set-your-splunk-credentials" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Export your credentials as environment variables. Replace each placeholder with your actual values:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2. Instrument with OBI</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/2-instrument-with-obi/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/2-instrument-with-obi/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Now add APM tracing to this running app &lt;strong&gt;without touching a single line of code&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="download-obi"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Download OBI&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#download-obi" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download the pre-built OBI binary from the &lt;a href="https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-ebpf-instrumentation/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;GitHub releases page &lt;span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:0.75em;opacity:0.6;"&gt;&amp;#x2197;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Look for this in your Output"&gt;Look for this in your Output&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-2" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-2" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-3" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-3" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Example Output"&gt;Example Output&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-4" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-4" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-5" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-5" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Look for this in your Output"&gt;Look for this in your Output&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-6" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-6" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-7" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-7" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Example Output"&gt;Example Output&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-8" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-8" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-9" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-9" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Look for this in your Output"&gt;Look for this in your Output&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-10" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-10" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-11" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-11" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Example Output"&gt;Example Output&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/workshop/obi/01-obi-python
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;sudo env &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_TRACES_ENDPOINT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;https://ingest.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;REALM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;.signalfx.com:443&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_TRACES_PROTOCOL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;grpc&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_HEADERS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;X-SF-Token=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;ACCESS_TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_SERVICE_NAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;warmup-app&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;deployment.environment=ebpf-bare-app,host.name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;INSTANCE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;OTEL_EBPF_OPEN_PORT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;5150&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; ./obi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Look for this in your Output"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Generate traffic and look for this output&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Verify in Splunk APM</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/3-verify-in-splunk/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/3-verify-in-splunk/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="check-splunk-apm"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Check Splunk APM&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#check-splunk-apm" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate to &lt;strong&gt;APM&lt;/strong&gt; in Splunk Observability Cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Filter by service name &lt;code&gt;warmup-app&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You should see traces for the &lt;code&gt;/hello&lt;/code&gt; endpoint.
&lt;strong&gt;NOTE: This may take a number of minutes to ingest the first traces&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-just-happened"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;What Just Happened?&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#what-just-happened" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Flask app is &amp;ldquo;naked&amp;rdquo; it has zero observability code. It only knows how to say hello and send a heartbeat metric.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OBI attached eBPF probes to the kernel&amp;rsquo;s networking stack and observed HTTP traffic flowing through your app&amp;rsquo;s process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OBI generated OpenTelemetry-compatible trace spans and sent them directly to Splunk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You just added distributed tracing to a running process from the kernel. No SDK, no code changes, no restart.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>